title: Is Xbox Dying...?
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be Xbox games potentially showing up to their competitors. While in my opinion this is a net positive for all of us, this is a clear sign that in the world of gaming, Microsoft isn't so concerned with the hardware they sell. Thanks for watching!
